::DeathStorm/Prowl::

DeathStorm rolls sharply to the left. He feels his shoulder and his fingers 
go across a deep slice. He looks at Suukie. The bot was obvioutly serious. 
Considering the other two maximals in the clearing, DeathStorm decides to 
play along.

"I will not fight a fellow maximal." He says.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl flies back to the maximal base. Checking on his wounds, he decides that 
they are not serious. He goes straight to whatever room Liono was talking 
about.
